character.name: Create a complete spritesheet of one astronaut crew member in pixel art style. Style: retro-modern pixel art, crisp edges, clean shading, coherent color palette, chibi-proportioned astronaut (32x48 sprite feel).  Layout: 4 directions (down, left, right, up) with walk cycle (4 frames per direction). Optionally allow 8 directions if supported.  Background: fully transparent.  Camera: orthographic isometric cam, consistent top-down pixel-art sprite style. Palette: neutral white suit, slightly weathered, with role-specific accents. Lighting: uniform and consistent across all frames, soft rim lighting. Do not include text, UI, logos, or additional objects. Only one consistent character across all frames.  Role-specific details: Medic — medical red chest panel (#E74C3C) with a white cross symbol, helmet stripe red, small medical kit on hip or chest, suit cleaner than others.
